1.7
log
@Use the new input functions of wsmouse in mouse and touchscreen drivers.

ok stsp@@ kettenis@@
@
text
@/*	$OpenBSD: ams.c,v 1.6 2011/06/15 21:32:05 miod Exp $	*/
/*	$NetBSD: ams.c,v 1.11 2000/12/19 03:13:40 tsubai Exp $	*/

